notes: Ceruloplasmin binds to membrane receptors on the surface of RBC membranes, which was later shown to be SLC40A1 transporter protein (pubmed:6095836;pubmed:23219802;pubmed:2835996).
MPO binds to RBC membranes in vitro and in vivo and RBCs may avidly bind circulating MPO, and may act as carriers of this leukocyte-derived enzyme (pubmed:24976018)
